text: Bishtyubinka () is a rural locality (a selo) in Starokucherganovsky Selsoviet, Narimanovsky District, Astrakhan Oblast, Russia. The population was 1,117 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 8.3 km from Astrakhan, 49 km from Narimanov. == References == Category:Rural localities in Narimanovsky District
title: Bishtyubinka
